OL,3,CFlat 'grossly overcrowded' ahead of
OL,4,Cfatal e-bike fire, court told
OL,6,FA husband and wife landlord team
OL,7,Frented out a "grossly overcrowded"
OL,8,Feast London flat where an e-bike fire
OL,9,Fled to the death of a tenant, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FFather-of-two Mizanur Rahman, 41, died
OL,13,Ffrom the effects of smoke inhalation
OL,14,Fafter the fire in the early hours of
OL,15,FMarch 5 2023 at Maddocks House in
OL,16,FShadwell.
OL,18,FParents-of-six Sofina Begum, 52, and
OL,19,FAminur Rahman, 55, had previously
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to a total of nine
OL,21,Fhousing offences.
