OL,3,CFlat 'grossly overcrowded' ahead of
OL,4,Cfatal e-bike fire, court told
OL,6,FJudge Emma Smith, sitting at
OL,7,FSnaresbrook Crown Court, said she was
OL,8,Flooking at sentencing the couple, of
OL,9,FWapping, east London, not on the
OL,10,Ffatality or the fire, but on the
OL,11,Fhousing offences which they pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to in November 2023. This could
OL,13,Fmean a fine.
OL,15,FGemma Gillett, for Tower Hamlets
OL,16,FCouncil, who brought the case, told
OL,17,Fthe court: "It is clear that the
OL,18,Fproperty was, and had been
OL,19,Fconsiderably for some time, grossly
OL,20,Fovercrowded.
