OL,3,CFlat 'grossly overcrowded' ahead of
OL,4,Cfatal e-bike fire, court told
OL,6,F"The information available suggests
OL,7,Fthat some 23 people were in occupation
OL,8,Fof the flat. One of the occupants was
OL,9,Ftaken to hospital and subsequently
OL,10,Fdied."
OL,12,FTenants were told not to use the flat
OL,13,Fas a postal address as it could get
OL,14,Fthe couple in trouble, the court heard.
OL,16,FFormer residents of the flat have said
OL,17,Fthey paid about #90 a week, where some
OL,18,Fshared beds or slept on the floor of
OL,19,Fthe two-bedroom ex-council flat. There
OL,20,Fwere 18 beds, including bunk beds, at
OL,21,Fthe property.
