OL,6,FBut one of the residents told liaison
OL,7,Fofficers that he paid rent to Rahman.
OL,9,FMs Gillett said: "At this point, Mr
OL,10,FRahman claimed not to speak English
OL,11,Fand the conversation ended."
OL,13,FShe said the "overall picture was of a
OL,14,Fproperty of longer term occupiers and
OL,15,Ftransient individuals".
OL,17,FThe property has been repossessed by
OL,18,Fthe bank.
