OL,6,FThe judge noted that a month after the
OL,7,Ffire, Begum made an application for an
OL,8,Fextension of the lost space which did
OL,9,Fnot mention the fire or that the
OL,10,Fproperty was uninhabitable, and said
OL,11,Fshe was living at the flat and it was
OL,12,Fovercrowded.
OL,14,FThe judge also noted that this event
OL,15,Ftook place after the charges she was
OL,16,Fdealing with.
OL,18,FThe defendants say that a "rogue
OL,19,Fmanager", who is called Mr Raja,
OL,20,Fhelped them with the property but
OL,21,Fprosecutors say this person is Rahman.
